00:08.008 --> 00:12.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight: From
his income
taxes to his foundation, Donald
Trump faces

00:12.980 --> 00:18.285 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
