terrorist group
out of the country forever.

00:39.640 --> 00:45.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: This road is the
front line
before getting to
ISIS-controlled Mosul, and

00:45.579 --> 00:50.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
all along the front line here,
it is divided
up between the various groups
who are fighting

00:50.817 --> 00:52.619 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
ISIS.

00:52.653 --> 00:56.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Plus: ahead of
tomorrow night's
debate, a look at the two vice
presidential

00:56.056 --> 01:01.728 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
nominees and what to expect in a
Mike Pence/Tim
Kaine showdown.

01:01.762 --> 01:04.197 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
All that and more on tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

01:04.231 --> 01:08.402 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
(BREAK)

01:08.435 --> 01:20.514 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Thirty-six days
to go, and
the Trump campaign is struggling
again to

01:20.547 --> 01:22.382 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
get back on message.

01:22.416 --> 01:28.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Instead, questions about Donald
Trump's taxes,
treatment of women and even his
charity swirled

01:28.155 --> 01:31.158 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
today, and his opponent was
quick to strike.

01:31.191 --> 01:33.827 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
John Yang has our report.

01:33.860 --> 01:40.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Hillary Clinton
pounced on reports
that Donald Trump might have
avoid income

01:40.767 --> 01:47.374 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
taxes because of business losses
to suggest
he may not be the businessman he
says he is.

01:47.407 --> 01:50.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON (D),
Presidential Candidate:
Yesterday, his campaign was
bragging it makes

01:50.744 --> 01:51.712 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
him a genius.

01:51.745 --> 01:52.713 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

01:52.746 --> 01:54.114 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON: Here's
my question.

01:54.147 --> 01:58.085 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What kind of genius loses a
billion dollars
in a single year?

01:58.118 --> 01:59.820 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(CHEERING AND APPLAUSE)

01:59.853 --> 02:06.460 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON: This is
Trump to a
T. He's taking corporate excess
and made a

02:06.493 --> 02:08.295 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
business model out of it.

02:08.328 --> 02:13.667 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: The New York Times
published part
of Trump's 1995 federal tax
return showing

02:13.700 --> 02:21.208 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
