would like
to sleep with, and made lewd
comments about

03:47.661 --> 03:49.996 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
women on the show and on the
crew.

03:50.030 --> 03:54.334 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the New York state attorney
general, a
Democrat who is backing Clinton,
ordered the

03:54.367 --> 04:00.073 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Trump Foundation to stop
fund-raising in the
state, saying it's not properly
registered.

04:00.107 --> 04:05.679 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
In addition, Trump was
criticized for comments
made about PTSD sufferers at a
forum with

04:05.712 --> 04:07.481 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
