04:07.514 --> 04:09.950 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP (R), Presidential
Candidate:
When you talk about the mental
health problems,

04:09.983 --> 04:14.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
when people come back from war
and combat
and they see things that maybe a
lot of the

04:14.888 --> 04:18.258 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
folks in this room have seen
many times over,
and you're strong and you can
handle it, but

04:18.291 --> 04:20.127 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a lot of people can't handle it.

04:20.160 --> 04:23.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Later, the Marine who
asked the
question said he found Trump's
answer thoughtful

04:23.897 --> 04:25.532 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and understanding.

04:25.565 --> 04:30.170 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Republican vice presidential
hopeful Mike
Pence campaigned in Virginia.

04:30.203 --> 04:33.673 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
