U.S. failure
to meet its obligations under
the agreement.

05:30.931 --> 05:37.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hurricane Matthew bore down on
Haiti, with
winds of 140 miles per hour and
up to 40 inches

05:37.304 --> 05:38.505 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
of rain.

05:38.538 --> 05:41.575 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's one of the strongest
Atlantic storms
in recent years.

05:41.608 --> 05:47.047 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, late today, it was centered
about 230
miles southwest of
Port-au-Prince, the Haitian

05:47.080 --> 05:48.915 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
capital.

05:48.949 --> 05:53.653 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Outer bands of wind and rain
were already
battering the impoverished
country's southwestern

05:53.687 --> 05:55.055 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
tip.

05:55.088 --> 05:59.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The eye is expected to pass
near, or over,
that area late tonight.

05:59.259 --> 06:04.798 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The state of Ohio will resume
executing condemned
prisoners in January.

06:04.831 --> 06:10.036 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
