general's office
said that it now has a new
three-drug combination.

06:16.476 --> 06:21.915 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Attorneys for death row inmates
immediately
said they will file a new court
challenge.

06:21.948 --> 06:27.454 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Los Angeles police are facing
protests over
a fatal shooting on Saturday.

06:27.487 --> 06:33.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
