officer-involved
shooting occurred.

07:01.154 --> 07:05.692 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Beck also
defended police actions
in a second fatal shooting.

07:05.725 --> 07:11.031 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
