what turned
out to be a replica handgun at
officers, and

07:11.064 --> 07:12.832 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
they opened fire.

07:12.866 --> 07:18.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The U.S. Supreme Court opened
its fall term
today, and refused a White House
appeal to

07:18.038 --> 07:20.307 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
rehear a key immigration case.

07:20.340 --> 07:25.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
