the plan
remains in effect.

07:31.051 --> 07:36.823 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The court has had only eight
members since
Justice Antonin Scalia died in
March.

07:36.856 --> 07:42.996 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This was Black Monday in Poland,
with thousands
of women wearing black and
protesting against

07:43.029 --> 07:46.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
