Warsaw.

07:55.875 --> 08:00.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Poland is heavily Catholic, and
already has
one of the most restrictive
abortion laws

08:00.213 --> 08:01.581 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in Europe.

08:01.614 --> 08:06.753 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
