predictions it would
win easily.

10:04.604 --> 10:08.374 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CLAUDIA, Colombia (through
translator): We
have all been victims of the
FARC and this

10:08.408 --> 10:13.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
