challenging and the
living conditions a lot more
difficult.

28:17.162 --> 28:18.797 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So it's really a race against
time.

28:18.830 --> 28:23.468 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: Despite the
hardship, it's
better than living under ISIS
rule.

28:23.502 --> 28:28.907 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): Life
is miserable
here, but better than where we
were before.

28:28.941 --> 28:31.910 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
A price cannot be set for
freedom.

28:31.944 --> 28:33.712 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
