Virginia Senator
Tim Kaine may not be as
well-known or as polarizing

36:37.162 --> 36:39.130 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
as the candidates at the top of
the ticket.

36:39.164 --> 36:43.968 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In fact, polls show more than
one-third of
registered voters don't know
enough about

36:44.002 --> 36:48.740 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
