large Irish-Catholic
family.

37:41.926 --> 37:43.695 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

37:43.728 --> 37:47.832 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIKE PENCE: I'm really just a
small-town boy
who grew up in Southern Indiana
with a big

37:47.866 --> 37:49.767 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
