backyard.

37:49.801 --> 37:55.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Kaine grew up in
Kansas city,
Missouri, the elder of two
brothers, his father

37:55.640 --> 37:58.109 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
