teacher.

37:58.143 --> 37:59.978 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

38:00.011 --> 38:02.847 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TIM KAINE: I wanted to be a man
for others,
somebody who fought for the
rights of others,

38:02.881 --> 38:06.251 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
had others' back, would stand up
for others,
especially if others wouldn't.

38:06.284 --> 38:11.990 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Catholic
Church played
an integral role in both men's
early lives.

38:12.023 --> 38:18.630 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
