for The Richmond
Times-Dispatch for more than a
decade.

38:26.004 --> 38:30.041 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFF SCHAPIRO, The Richmond
Times-Dispatch:
I think the Jesuit connection is
important

38:30.074 --> 38:37.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
