45:35.733 --> 45:36.701 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
How much is at stake?

45:36.734 --> 45:38.102 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Yes.

45:38.135 --> 45:39.804 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
