on the campaign
trail throughout the course of
this campaign.

45:56.053 --> 45:59.590 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, as you pointed out, these
are already
two candidates that aren't
particularly known.

45:59.624 --> 46:04.428 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, look, I think the stakes
are pretty high
here, especially for Mike Pence.

46:04.462 --> 46:10.201 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It is going to be his challenge
tomorrow night
to keep the attention away from
all the problems

46:10.234 --> 46:14.038 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
