so, many of which have been
self-inflicted,

46:14.071 --> 46:22.179 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and to focus back on the issues
and the message
that Trump and the Trump
campaign would like

46:22.213 --> 46:26.884 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to be focused on, mainly to
prosecute the
case against Hillary Clinton,
Barack Obama

46:26.917 --> 46:28.653 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and the path forward.

46:28.686 --> 46:31.989 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, so, Tam, if
