46:33.824 --> 46:36.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: Well,
he has to come out and not have
any sunlight

46:36.294 --> 46:41.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
between himself and Hillary
Clinton, which
