falling in

46:41.532 --> 46:43.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
line.

46:43.334 --> 46:47.905 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They didn't necessarily agree on
TPP, but,
by the time he was announced as
V.P., he -- they

46:47.938 --> 46:49.674 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
