46:49.707 --> 46:55.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think also he intends to
come out and
try to show separation between
Mike Pence

46:55.780 --> 47:02.753 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and Donald Trump, and show that
there are
areas where Pence and Trump do
not see eye

47:02.787 --> 47:08.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to eye, where, you know, Pence
has said that
this isn't a name-calling kind
of campaign,

47:08.559 --> 47:11.228 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
at the same time that Donald
Trump was calling
people names on Twitter.

47:11.262 --> 47:15.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, and we know
vice presidential
debates may get attention at the
time, but

47:15.099 --> 47:17.568 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
