great deal
of effect.

47:17.601 --> 47:18.569 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
But we will see.

47:18.602 --> 47:20.104 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
AMY WALTER: Yes.

47:20.137 --> 47:23.574 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
No, I think there's still --
