of this debate?

47:36.287 --> 47:39.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, you both
have referred
to Donald Trump's controversies
of the last

47:39.156 --> 47:42.526 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
