to affect
this campaign?

47:57.675 --> 48:00.344 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: This is a
fascinating question
to me.

48:00.377 --> 48:05.216 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
