saying, yes,
I took advantage of the system.

48:18.095 --> 48:19.330 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's the system.

48:19.363 --> 48:21.465 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I can fix it because I know
the system.

48:21.499 --> 48:29.640 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And this $900 million loss in a
single year
is part of his story.

48:29.673 --> 48:33.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's part of the story that he's
been telling
about himself, that he went on
tough times

48:33.677 --> 48:38.883 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
