up and was
able to become this successful
businessman

48:38.916 --> 48:41.852 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
once again from the ashes of his
previous
businesses.

48:41.886 --> 48:47.458 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, it's unclear whether this
changes the
narrative in any way.

48:47.491 --> 48:52.296 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it almost feeds the story
that Donald
Trump has been telling about
himself all along.

48:52.329 --> 48:54.131 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Is that how you
see it?

48:54.165 --> 48:56.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Yes, or that's it's
