that should
hurt a traditional candidate.

49:19.290 --> 49:22.459 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Obviously, somebody like Mitt
Romney was by
making these statements.

49:22.493 --> 49:23.894 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Severely by it.

49:23.928 --> 49:25.696 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Severely by this.

49:25.729 --> 49:28.098 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And yet he still has tremendous
support among
people who see him as a success,
and to the

49:28.132 --> 49:34.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
point that Tam made, that he's
saying the
only person who can destroy the
system, a

49:34.271 --> 49:37.074 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
