benefited
from a rigged system.

49:37.107 --> 49:39.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let's talk
quickly about
some of the other stories that
have been out

49:39.944 --> 49:42.313 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
