demeaning remarks against a
number of them,

49:52.356 --> 49:54.158 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
used sexist language.

49:54.191 --> 49:59.129 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Amy, and the ongoing story about
Miss Universe,
that is something that has just
dominated

49:59.163 --> 50:02.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the news for the last number of
